<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="miracle-n">miracle <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˈmɪrəkl/    美 /ˈmɪrəkl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-wonder">1.<strong>[用单数] [非正式用语] 奇迹；不平凡的事；意外的幸运事(wonder)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>miracle cure / drug</strong>
有奇效的疗法 / 特效药</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>perform / work miracles</strong>
创造奇迹；有奇效</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>It's a miracle that</strong> these buildings came through the war undamaged.
这些建筑物历经战争却完好无损，真是个奇迹。</p></div></div>